videos.description: Clemson forward Aamir Simms collects the no-look pass from Marcquise Reed for the layup.
videos.headline: No-look pass leads to Clemson layup

videos.description: Pittsburgh big man Terrell Brown sends back the Clemson shot at one end and shows off the post moves on the other.
videos.headline: Brown's rejection leads to basket on other end

videos.description: Clemson's Gabe DeVoe hits a 3-pointer from the logo near half court padding the Tiger's lead.
videos.headline: Tigers' DeVoe drills 3 from logo

videos.description: Pittsburgh's unselfish play leads to a wide open 3-pointer for guard Parker Stewart.
videos.headline: Pitt shows off ball movement for open 3

videos.description: Clemson big man Elijah Thomas stuffs Terrell Brown's shot as the shot clock expires.
videos.headline: Clemson's denial forces shot clock violation

videos.description: Clemson head coach Brad Brownell explains his team's hot play of late and their play vs Pittsburgh.
videos.headline: Clemson's Brownell thought 'we were really ready to play'

videos.description: Clemson guard Gabe DeVoe breaks down his night, his thoughts on Donte Grantham's injury, and being ranked.
videos.headline: DeVoe: Wanted to open it up in second half

videos.description: Clemson guard Gabe DeVoe drills seven 3-pointers on his way to a 25 point night.
videos.headline: DeVoe shows off range with barrage of 3s
